    <assets>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia511.00">
            <value key="en">(Nidia's really distraught...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia511.01">
            <value key="en">I want to say something...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia511.02">
            <value key="en">But the atmosphere is so heavy...)</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia512.00">
            <value key="en">Nidia... I feel like there's something I'm missing here...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia513.00">
            <value key="en">You said you had to combine with someone to save the world... I know the road will be hard, but it also sounds like...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia514.00">
            <value key="en">Well, like a great adventure.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia515.00">
            <value key="en">You're going to get to do and see so much.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia515.01">
            <value key="en">But every once in a while your expression changes when you talk about it.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia516.00">
            <value key="en">Is there something you haven't said?</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia517.00">
            <value key="en">${slot:playerName}, I...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia517.01">
            <value key="en">................</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia518.00">
            <value key="en">It's okay... You don't have to talk about it. I just thought...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia519.00">
            <value key="en">No, I do.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia519.01">
            <value key="en">${slot:playerName}, I don't WANT to combine with anyone.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia519.02">
            <value key="en">But a prophecy is like a set of rules... For it to come true, you have to follow the guidelines.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia520.00">
            <value key="en">It says I have to combine with someone, and I just... Don't want to. I mean, if that's what it takes to save the world, I will, but...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia521.00">
            <value key="en">Go on....</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia522.00">
            <value key="en">I have to save the world, ${slot:playerName}. So I have to do what the prophecy says in order to fulfill it. But if the world IS saved... The last part of the prophecy says....</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia523.00">
            <value key="en">...................</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia524.00">
            <value key="en">What does it say?</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia525.00">
            <value key="en">The prophecy says that in order to save the world... I have to die.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia526.00">
            <value key="en">WHAT!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia527.00">
            <value key="en">I feel terrible complaining... I should rise to meet the challenge. The fate of the world is at stake.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia528.00">
            <value key="en">But it just feels so unfair...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia529.00">
            <value key="en">It's TOTALLY unfair!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia529.01">
            <value key="en">Who wrote this stupid prophecy!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia529.02">
            <value key="en">I'll roll them up and throw them into the sun!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia529.03">
            <value key="en">How do they like THAT prophecy!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia530.00">
            <value key="en">Haha...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia530.01">
            <value key="en">Hahahahahaa!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia530.02">
            <value key="en">${slot:playerName}!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia530.03">
            <value key="en">Some ancient oracle is turning over in his grave right now!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia531.00">
            <value key="en">Well, maybe they shouldn't have made such a dumb prophecy!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia532.00">
            <value key="en">Hahahahaha! ${slot:playerName}...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia533.00">
            <value key="en">Hahahaha!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia533.01">
            <value key="en">You're very sweet.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia534.00">
            <value key="en">No! I'm mad! I'm super mad!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia535.00">
            <value key="en">A prophecy is just a way to control a person! You have to do something because you fear the consequences.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia535.01">
            <value key="en">It's so wrong!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia536.00">
            <value key="en">Thank you, ${slot:playerName}.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia537.00">
            <value key="en">Listen... I don't want you to feel sorry for me or anything. I'd hate that.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia537.01">
            <value key="en">I know what I have to do.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia538.00">
            <value key="en">Still... I wish I knew what to say...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia539.00">
            <value key="en">BE TRUE TO YOURSELF.......</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia540.00">
            <value key="en">But I have to be true to the prophecy...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia541.00">
            <value key="en">.... BE TRUE TO YOURSELF....</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia542.00">
            <value key="en">Nidia... Pac-Man's right.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia542.01">
            <value key="en">You always have a hard time deciding what to think.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia543.00">
            <value key="en">I know you think that's bad, but...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia543.01">
            <value key="en">You know what I think?</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia544.00">
            <value key="en">I think it means you believe in the power of possibility.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia544.01">
            <value key="en">You always have more than one way of seeing a situation.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia545.00">
            <value key="en">Shouldn't you look at this prophecy the same way? Maybe it's not your life you have to question... But the prophecy itself.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia545.01">
            <value key="en">Maybe combining means accepting every part of yourself... The good AND the bad... And being happy with it.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia546.00">
            <value key="en">Maybe you don't NEED someone else to make the amulet work.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia547.00">
            <value key="en">Maybe ... I'm free to choose... How to choose!</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia548.00">
            <value key="en">You can choose to partner up with someone...</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia548.01">
            <value key="en">Or not.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia548.02">
            <value key="en">It's completely up to you.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia549.00">
            <value key="en">Don't let some old book tell you how to live, Nidia.</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia550.00">
            <value key="en">...................</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia551.00">
            <value key="en">${slot:playerName}..........</value>
        </TextAsset>
        <TextAsset key="t_snidia552.00">
            <value key="en">Thank you.</value>
        </TextAsset>
